description:
When Lexy Swallow decided to move, there were plenty of moving companies she could have called, but one stood out above the rest. At the C & C Moving, they treat any and every box like it was made of gold, and know just how to handle them. At C & C Moving, they'll make sure your box is properly filled, and will not stop until every box in the house is taken care of. And they know how to finish the job. Your satisfaction is guaranteed, and your your box is our pleasure.

Enjoy!
title: Handle My Box With Care
